@startuml sd_ExcelService_exportToExcel
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title ExcelService.exportToExcel(records) - 导出工资明细Excel

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "PayrollController" as Ctrl
participant "ExcelService" as ExcelSvc
participant "Workbook\n(XSSFWorkbook)" as Wb
participant "Sheet" as Sheet
participant "CellStyle" as Style
participant "SalaryRecord\n(实体)" as Rec

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/payroll/export?yearMonth=202403
Ctrl -> ExcelSvc: exportToExcel(records)
note right of ExcelSvc #F0F8FF
  **导出流程:**
  1. 创建XSSFWorkbook
  2. 创建"工资明细"Sheet
  3. 创建表头样式(grey背景)
end note
ExcelSvc -> Wb: new XSSFWorkbook()
ExcelSvc -> Wb: createSheet("工资明细")
Wb --> ExcelSvc: Sheet
ExcelSvc -> Wb: createCellStyle()
ExcelSvc -> Style: setFillForegroundColor(GREY)
ExcelSvc -> Sheet: createRow(0)
note right of ExcelSvc #F0F8FF
  **表头:**
  工资号 | 姓名 | 部门
  应发合计 | 个税 | 社保
  公积金 | 实发合计
end note
loop SalaryRecord | 每行
  ExcelSvc -> Sheet: createRow(rn++)
  ExcelSvc -> Rec: getEmployee().getEmployeeNo()
  ExcelSvc -> Rec: getEmployee().getName()
  ExcelSvc -> Rec: getEmployee().getDepartment().getName()
  ExcelSvc -> Rec: getGrossPay() / getIncomeTax()
  ExcelSvc -> Rec: getSocialInsurance() / getHousingFund()
  ExcelSvc -> Rec: getNetPay()
end
ExcelSvc -> ExcelSvc: autoSizeColumn(i) for each
ExcelSvc -> Wb: write(bos)
ExcelSvc --> Ctrl: byte[] (Excel二进制)
note right of Ctrl : ResponseEntity → Content-Disposition: attachment;\nfilename=工资明细_202403.xlsx
Ctrl --> Client: Excel文件下载
@enduml
